{"tid":2002669,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"無綫門口再現橫額稱楊秀惠是老千　標題是「十八年後的千局告白」","createTime":"2020-05-05T10:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T10:22:25.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"192e298d7dac01940cbd82af2be91c52bd462845","tid":2002669,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:21:47.000Z","msg":"楊秀惠最近在《十八年後的終極告白》中有亮麗演出，不少觀眾大讚她演技進步，不過今日又被是非纏身！事緣有讀者報料指於TVB將軍澳電視城的門口，見到一幅寫著以「十八年後的千局告白」為題的橫額，內容矛頭直指楊秀惠。<br />\n<br />\n據報料人士表示，該橫額於今日（5日）下午約2時出現，現場有數人在圍觀但未見有人動手拆除。其實楊秀惠今年年初已被同樣事情纏繞，當時同樣在電視城門口，有人掛了一塊10米長的巨型Banner同撒街招，內容指楊秀惠的妹妹以及妹夫為詐騙集團的首腦，成立的美容院也是用作洗黑錢，而楊秀惠和妹妹的照片也在街招當中。<br />\n<br />\n當時楊秀惠發出了聲明，指自己並不了解妹妹的生活，而她的美容生意也由她一人獨資，妹妹並無投資任何資金。最後她也表示，如果妹妹有犯法，一定會大義滅親，絕不姑息！並說：「請各位的華洋轇輵，不要把我牽涉當中！謝謝！」<br />\n<br />\n今次「十八年後的千局告白」的橫額內容指楊秀惠講大話，雖然口說與妹妹割蓆，但其實早年親口承認自己與妹妹有合作生意，更有嚴重指控是洗黑錢。"},{"pid":"3a4f16a4b6a6335b16500fd32809f9d8caad5463","tid":2002669,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4436443/org/dd1c66cac14a0dead730c2a3ba8fbe49.jpeg/VF5zhGXdH4hEBHQKDchwpWEN2dB2_u6HUv8Pv1L_D78?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4436443%2Forg%2Fdd1c66cac14a0dead730c2a3ba8fbe49.jpeg%2FVF5zhGXdH4hEBHQKDchwpWEN2dB2_u6HUv8Pv1L_D78%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=27806181&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19589bf924cb7134c14c6b26247cf0045a54ade1","tid":2002669,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4436352/org/d7f7a57a917735258ba764829f1c2269.jpg/7zsuo_OVrYXzHjnwWxk_ObblCqLEwPSatqd5HLaneRw?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4436352%2Forg%2Fd7f7a57a917735258ba764829f1c2269.jpg%2F7zsuo_OVrYXzHjnwWxk_ObblCqLEwPSatqd5HLaneRw%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=75221289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在年頭出現的橫額。（網上圖片）"},{"pid":"3559b54f2bd9386981e10f5caca108cd0b499c81","tid":2002669,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4436363/org/ed2a4e8aae3ca9bf61a510b1531fb2b8.jpeg/PmX4TKwKvGNebKJ1zkZjOlAkMI9L4EyRuarbPrmq2z4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4436363%2Forg%2Fed2a4e8aae3ca9bf61a510b1531fb2b8.jpeg%2FPmX4TKwKvGNebKJ1zkZjOlAkMI9L4EyRuarbPrmq2z4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=37927ede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次又有街招，更有楊秀惠妹夫的身分證。（報料人提供）"}]}